title: Ep 15 | Craziest Things People Have Told Hair Stylists!
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
As you know (or maybe not?!) Jenna and Brooklin are hair stylists and as hairstylists, you hear just about everything under the sun. You become your client's therapist in a sense. We've collected some of your craziest stories and they share theirs! Have a crazy story to tell? Share it in the comments!

Wondering where our other episodes are?? The Video versions are on Kristen's channel here: http://www.youtube.com/Kristenxleanne. We're also on Spotify, Apple Podcast and more!
